* An instance of this class is a ListResourceBundle that * has the required getContents() method that returns * an array of message-key/message associations. *

* The message keys are defined in {@link MsgKey}. The * messages that those keys map to are defined here. *

* The messages in the English version are intended to be * translated. * * This class is not a public API, it is only public because it is * used in org.apache.xml.serializer. * * @xsl.usage internal

methods.name: public Object[][] getContents()
methods.comment: The lookup table for error messages.
